              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SISD"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "A large-area multistrip dE-E telescope was",
                "positioned close to the focal plane of TwinSol to",
                "identify and track tritons. It consists of two 500",
                "mu-m thick silicon-pad detectors (5 x 5 cm2) that are",
                "segmented into four pads each to form a 16-pixel",
                "telescope. Low-energy silicon-strip array (LESA) was",
                "used to detect the low-energy a particles from the",
                "decay of the excited states in 19Ne. The array consists",
                "of six identical 300 mu-m thick silicon-pad",
                "detectors, each with four pads of a size of 4 x 4 cm2."
              ]
            }
